[schema van cijfer uit het jaartal, 6x]: 8. In favour of Bruegel speaks: not only the quality of the painting in the roe, but the close relation to the roe drawn in Tolnay 123 (verso of T.100) in Rijksmuseum. I cannot find the [schema] for 5 in any of Bruegel's drawings. The V of BRVEGEL is ususally [Schema V] not [schema] but with the first stroke stressed and with little horizontal strokes at the top, but the V in T. 31 is omitted [scan].
